{"type": "article", "id": 16374, "title": "安吉丽娜·朱莉全家拍大片，以及， 万圣节冰激凌有点好看｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2015-10-21T09:15:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2855, "name": "Tommy Hilfiger"}, {"id": 16038, "name": "BAPE"}, {"id": 1508, "name": "Net-a-porter"}, {"id": 11593, "name": "Yoox"}, {"id": 17552, "name": "Frette"}, {"id": 17553, "name": "APC"}, {"id": 1330, "name": "ASOS"}, {"id": 2840, "name": "Opening Ceremony"}, {"id": 13245, "name": "水原希子"}, {"id": 12272, "name": "Ben & Jerry"}, {"id": 1817, "name": "纪梵希"}, {"id": 955, "name": "VOGUE"}, {"id": 13757, "name": "Bang & Olufsen"}, {"id": 3813, "name": "碧昂斯"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 75588, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 78, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605221157ZJYBG4PCtXe0Fnbj.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t一些重要的新闻：\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/specialty-stores/tommy-hilfigers-virtual-reality-play-10265078/\" target=\"_blank\"></a></strong><strong><a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/specialty-stores/tommy-hilfigers-virtual-reality-play-10265078/\" target=\"_blank\">Tommy Hilfiger 开发虚拟现实游戏</a>｜</strong>第五大道的旗舰店内，消费者从下周二开始就能够店铺内用 VR 头戴式设备观看新季走秀了，360 度无死角哦。之后会在伦敦、巴黎、米兰等城市推出。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong><a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/direct-internet-catalogue/yoox-net-a-porter-group-restructuring-10265328/\" target=\"_blank\">Yoox Net-a-porter 内部重组</a>｜</strong>创意工作室的成员，包括摄影师、摄像师、造型师、文案等人将一周只上四天班，时间从早上 8 点到晚上 6 点半。两个时尚电商巨头合并后的重组将会影响到 400 位员工，但对消费者并没有影响。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/textiles/frette-bespoke-service-milan-10264982/\" target=\"_blank\">奢侈家具品牌 </a></strong><span><strong><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/textiles/frette-bespoke-service-milan-10264982/\" target=\"_blank\">Frette 推出定制服务</a>｜</strong><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/textiles/frette-bespoke-service-milan-10264982/\" target=\"_blank\"></a>率先在米兰的<span style=\"text-align:left;\">斯皮加街旗舰店内推出，之后会扩展到巴黎、纽约的旗舰店内。定制服务涵盖了所有的项目，</span>包括床单、毛巾、毛毯、睡衣等，定制可选择的项目多达 3 万种，比如面料、颜色、花纹等等，价格在原来基础上提高 30% 左右，定制时间为四到八周。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/mergers-acquisitions/a-p-c-invests-in-outer-voices-10265761/\" target=\"_blank\">法国时装品牌 APC 投资 </a></strong><span><strong><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/mergers-acquisitions/a-p-c-invests-in-outer-voices-10265761/\" target=\"_blank\">Outdoor Voices</a>｜</strong></span><strong></strong>后者是美国运动品牌，明年将推出两个品牌的联名款。前者成立于 2013 年，刚获得 700 万美元融资。这牌子挺优雅，<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/16336.html\" target=\"_blank\">具体可以见 10 月 20 日的好奇心报道。</a></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong><a href=\"http://www.nofashion.cn/a/1445322277892.html\" target=\"_blank\">ASOS 全年盈利增 1%</a></strong><strong></strong><strong>｜</strong>英国最大时尚电商 ASOS 2015 财年成功从 2014 财年一连串盈利预警的低谷中反弹，实现符合市场预期的盈利，零售收入亦突破 10 亿英镑，集团预测当前 2016 财年将继续录得 20% 的较快收入增长。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><a href=\"http://www.nofashion.cn/a/1445313965427.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Furla 上半年收入攀升 30%</strong><strong></strong></a><strong>｜</strong>截至 6 月 30 日的前 6 个月收入同比攀升 30% 至 1.515 亿欧元，升幅比 2014 年全年的 13% 进步明显。可比收入增速达 22%，使零售收入占比从 2014 的 60% 上升至 65%。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t一些值得一看的：\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t水原希子为 Opening Ceremony 拍摄 2015 年秋冬系列 lookbook\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052211374gktRxUuLA70vwSI.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.49846154\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221138ZNG3z2lSOcHMauvo.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.38153846\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221138RaV9LQcU0e3hIfuW.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.41384615\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221139enxsOJB6yAb0HCjV.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.49076923\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221139vAUMQudy82itqjaF.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.38153846\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221140L3VahYuGfpxBwP9b.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.41384615\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221140IvdVxJ14skUH3RGX.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.38153846\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221141ETCVbGKRsw1iJ47u.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.38153846\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t纪梵希的 2016 年春夏系列眼镜，纪梵希负责创意，Safilo 公司负责制造。总共分为四个系列，有 RAVE（表现年轻前卫）、STYLE（表现建筑灵感）、ICON（表现纪梵希基因）和 STAR（表现永恒造型）。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052211415iqKoWNvBkt2JHTR.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052211420uX68W3Hx2BldNmQ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221142zPKdjo7yZs4RIOVC.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052211436gs0leCZvBQmitPM.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221143GKuvOZzhiA01Vey3.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">Ben &amp; Jerry 推出万圣节主题冰激凌，在 10 月 13 日到同月 27 日售卖，看上去简直不忍心下勺。这是日本限定款哦，所以这段时间去日本的不要错过哦。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221143CzVi3Mh7QfPdruqT.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221144kXUQVuRDG2xpB1Ir.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221144TtBmZPOVyWofpgYJ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221145DPax170twS4LuYmy.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t安吉丽娜·朱莉、布拉德·皮特一家登上 VOGUE 11 月封面，她站在海边的场景呼应了自编自导自演的电影《By the sea》。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052211455Q3JDswceS6zGiun.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052211463FERTdD5xWHMnpgi.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221146Hk7cAiey1j48BVa5.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221147H0jkKAy8EZ3MFbLp.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t继 BeoPlay H6 之后，音响大厂 Bang &amp; Olufsen 推出进阶版的新款无线耳机 BeoPlay H7。功能上不仅可以蓝芽连接你的音响或手机，以无线方式使用，BeoPlay H7 仍有提供耳机线，想要节省电源的时候就只要轻松地插入你的音响装置，同时 B&amp;O 也宣称此款耳机可以提供连续 20 小时的电力，另外还有内建式的感应装置。目前 BeoPlay H7 已经可以在<a href=\"http://www.beoplay.com/products/beoplayh7?_ga=1.243174336.394423549.1445309703\">官方网站</a>上购买，售价约 329 英镑。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221148wU1xZakKpqz2DBvR.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221148kwjMAXu2UfbPa8n6.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t碧昂斯<span style=\"text-align:left;\">披着星条旗</span>为 BEAT 杂志拍摄封面。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221149x5bVaJ08oLtgF9vl.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66704289\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221149OxvlJAo5CRhzctjp.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.50326797\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052211490fyWE18rpcjnlBPv.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.50326797\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052211503UOyxmbY58ToGftQ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221150yuC2Qdf3SOMRPrUV.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\tChanel Cruise 2016 年早春度假系列的硬广照抢先看。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052211516IwRzCyOegV5HBak.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221152LvkNGKYwg37psXEd.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221152RHrxYpMkAEvSIlQs.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221153IXGm39KrE5BZjcxT.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221154nyNl43gGcJwV285Q.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221154NVeA4n32HhaEo1kC.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>AAPE by BAPE 与 <span>Pac-Man 合作，推出了一些关于吃豆人游戏的产品。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221155CTEPfYoFJi4smzxr.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.65555556\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221155X6HolOeK1AL78WGx.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.65555556\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052211561QCXevhGL6O9lqAk.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.65555556\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221157ey5KW9dtfR17HrLZ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.65555556\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\t一些有意思的说法：\r\n</h4>\r\n<p>\r\n\tNRF(<span>The National Retail Federation</span>) 调查报告称，今年是数字购物的一年。有 46％ 的人们选择在网上购物，去年的数字是 44.4%；37.9% 的受访者称会使用智能手机来研究产品，28.4% 的受访者称会使用智能手机寻找店铺的位置；<span>而平板电脑发挥着和智能手机相同的效用；</span>46.7% 的受访者称免费送货和促销活动是他们会选择购物的重要因素；人均计划支出也从原来的 802 美元上升到了 805 美元。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}